{"tid":1684152,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"前線手足係咪少咗即場小組討論傾行動？","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:46:42.000Z","uid":90735,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d0400d519f19377cd2b1f41771b040dc373d36","tid":1684152,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"手足被捉一個就少一個...<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得6月26日包圍律政中心，手足開小組討論，最後安全遊行去蘭桂芳<br />\n7月1日攻立法會，都係即場討論決定攻入立法會<br />\n自從8月開始有黑警玩臥底之後，有鬼喺討論帶風向，前線手足係咪開始少咗即場小組討論做啲乜？<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，大家一定要時時刻刻諗清楚<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行動目的</strong></span>，多一秒唔知做乜好就會行行企企，就會多一秒危險<br />\n<br />\n有巴打3個月前好有心咁寫咗檢討post，係時候重溫一下：<br />\n<br />\n首要目標︰<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先訂立行動目的</span></span><br />\n今日出黎係<span style=\"color: red;\">正面衝擊</span> / <span style=\"color: orange;\">遊擊</span> / <span style=\"color: green;\">和平散</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6kfmcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6kfmcc.jpg&h=854db373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382899/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382899/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚太子班狗一定會再玩快速包抄戰術，各位小心</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a2cdab70cc4990f74b49b5a00b151e9c494325d5","tid":1684152,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ed86c3bbd2a4e4c1a8fc0db73afab94b32edda","tid":1684152,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3250524e93ff378559f8b0aed454bd2e405b51e0","tid":1684152,"uid":191613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff672c7b8d6b8678bb668fb6b785a518c0d58883"